body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, my name is Joe Scott and I'm from AutoWorld, how may I assist you today? May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hi, my name is Kelly Jackson.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Kelly. Could you please provide me with your contact number, one zero three four, and your email address?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, my contact number is 1034 and my email address is kelly.jackson@example.com.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Kelly. Can you also share with me your current location, zip code two three one four five, and the model of car you are interested in?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: My current location is zip code 23145, and I'm interested in the latest SUV model.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for providing that information, Kelly. Our team will reach out to you shortly with available inventory options. Is there anything else I can help you with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, thank you. I'm just feeling a bit sad about not finding the car I want.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand, Kelly. Our goal is to make sure you find the perfect car for your needs. Thank you for sharing your concerns with us today. We will work hard to find the ideal car for you. Have a great day!

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Thank you for your help. Goodbye.
